RELEASE NOTES:
Nowares pressenterat SureThing CD/DVD Labeler Deluxe v.5.0.593.0
The new SureThing CD/DVD Labeler v5 Deluxe Edition is the easiest way to create 
stunning, professional-looking labels. Supports all major label brands, 
LightScribe and direct-to-disc inkjet printers.

Requirments
Windows 2000, XP or Vista 
Intel Pentium II (or compatible) 300MHz or faster processor
256MB of RAM 
800x600 monitor resolution, 16-bit video card recommended 
Windows-compatible inkjet or laser printer 64MB of available hard disk space 
CD-ROM drive 
LightScribe drive required to burn LightScribe discs
